Goal Title: Upskill in Azure and Container Technologies

Desired Goal: Develop proficiency in Azure App Configuration, Azure Functions, and container technologies to support cloud-native application development.

Specific Actions:





Complete training or certification in Azure App Configuration, Azure Functions, and container technologies (e.g., Docker, Kubernetes).



Apply skills by building a project integrating these technologies on Azure.



Share knowledge with the team through documentation or a presentation.



Stay informed on advancements in these technologies through regular review of relevant resources.

Measure of Success: The goal will be achieved when:





Training or certification in the specified technologies is completed.



A functional project integrating Azure ACA, Azure Functions, and containers is deployed.



Knowledge is shared with the team, receiving positive feedback.



Ongoing engagement with relevant technical resources is demonstrated.
